description:
"outfit in pandemic" 1

from collection "outfit in pandemic"

I feel like the virus has affected my refined taste, lockdowns, quarantines, bans have caused a brutal change in my wardrobe, as far as possible don't leave the house, as far as possible don't leave the car, sweatpants, a bathrobe and a big sweater is my only refuge...I just hope it won't be my permanent deformation, but just an artistic concept during the period of illness.-)
